I’d like to do is just submit it for the record to save time. But, also, 
I’d  like  to—I  have  an  airport  person  from  Texarkana,  Arkansas.  If 
I could submit their testimony for the record, as well. 

Senator BURNS. Without objection, we’ll certainly do that. 
